    {
      "id": 19,
      "title": "Funnel Reference",
      "description": "Quick reference for pipeline stages and expected behavior.",
      "type": "text",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Pipeline Stages\n\n| Stage | Metric | Healthy Range |\n|-------|--------|---------------|\n| Universe | `universe_size` | 20-40 |\n| Data Freshness | `data_age_seconds == 0` | >95% |\n| Alpha Generated | `signals_generated_total` | varies |\n| Confidence Passed | `signal_confidence_passed_total` | >10% of generated |\n| Risk Gate Pass | `risk_gate_pass_total` | >30% of inputs |\n| Orders Placed | `orders_placed_total` | >50% of risk-pass |\n\n**Debugging workflow:**\n1. Rejection Reasons (Row 4) → find top blocker\n2. AI Confidence (Row 3) → check if AI vetoing signals\n3. Kill Reasons (Row 3) → check early-stage drops\n4. Data Freshness (Row 2) → check for stale data"
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 37 }
    }
